She’s making history ♥️ @anitta @recordingacademy 

Grammy’s Best New Artist Nominee 

We wanted to mimic her gorgeous pink panther diamond necklace on her nails and come out with this stunning nail look 💖 

✨Nails Breakdown ✨

▫️Prep the nails

▫️OPI GelColor Stay Classic Base Coat

▫️One coat of OPI GelColor in Sugar Crush it

▫️One coat of OPI GelColor in I Meta My Soulmate from #MeMyselfandOPI 

▫️Apply a thin layer of OPI GelColor Stay Shiny Top Coat

▫️Wipe the stickiness off with alcohol 

▫️Rub the OPI Chrome Effects in Pay Me In Rubies

▫️Apply OPI GelColor Stay Shiny Top Coat 

Anitta’s dress for the Grammys was edgy but was accessorized with the pink panther diamond necklace, adding a bit of elegance. Pink diamonds are known to symbolize elegance and romance so we played off of that for the nail look with the star OPI shade being “I Meta My Soulmate” from the brand’s newest collection Me, Myself and OPI that truly embodied that.

VANESSA x OSCARS 2023 🖤 @vanessahudgens 
 
We wanted to do something classic and chic that compliments her vintage Chanel dress while being unique at the same time. Her classic look called for classic shades so it was only fitting that we used @opi “Black Onyx” and “Funny Bunny.” She loves adding a twist when it comes to her look and so while we did black and white nails, we spiced it up with a half reversed and half traditional french nails. 
 
✨Nails Breakdown ✨
▫️Prep the nails
▫️OPI GelColor Stay Classic Base Coat
▫️2 coats of OPI GelColor in Funny Bunny
▫️Draw a half traditional french and half reversed french tip and connect them with straight line in the middle using art brush and OPI GelColor in Black Onyx
▫️Apply OPI GelColor Stay Shiny Top Coat 
 
#OPIObsessed @opi_professional

Glowing in the dark @haileybieber 💚 
After trying 50 different colors, we came up with the perfect shade for Coachella 🔫 Always enjoy our scientific experiment 🫶🏻
 
How to get the look: @opi @opi_professionals 
 
Step 1: Apply Stay Strong GelColor Base Coat
Step 2: Mix OPI GelColor in No Faux Yellow and OPI GelColor in Green Come True with Stay Strong GelColor Base Coat. Add little bit of glow in the dark powder to the color and mix it well

Step 3: Apply one coat of mixed color and cure it
Step 4: Apply Stay Shiny GelColor Top Coat and cure it
Step 5: Draw squiggly lines using OPI GelColor in Suzy’s Slinging Mezcal and cure it
Step 6: Gently rub OPI Chrome Effects in Gold Digger on gold lines
Step 7: Apply Stay Shiny GelColor Top Coat and cure it
 
#OPIObsessed #AskForOPI #haileybiebernails #glowinthedarknails #coachellanails

@VanessaHudgens x @MichaelKors #MetGala2023 

Negative Space but make it Platinum Eclipse 🖤✨Michael Kors' vision for Vanessa's look was a galactic ballerina concept, and to complement her dress and makeup, we collaborated to create a design that would perfectly harmonize with the overall look. The detailed line in the middle of the nail with a subtle shimmer adds a sophisticated touch to her bold manicure.

 

Products I used: 

▫️ Apply one coat of OPI GelColor Stay Strong Base Coat

▫️ Apply 2 coats of OPI GelColor in #BlackOnyx using art brush leaving a negative straight line in the middle 

▫️ Apply one coat of OPI GelColor in #PlatinumEclipse on the negative line and manipulate it with magnet to make straight effect

▫️ Apply one coat of OPI GelColor Stay Shiny Top Coat

@madelyncline x @stellamccartney #MetGala2023

Glazed donut nails are back at Met Gala but this time with Fleur De Lis ⚜️ It was only fitting to bring the glazed donut nail look back for this year’s Met Gala, knowing that that’s where the trend began! This time, we put a spin on it using another classic and iconic shade from OPI, Bare My Soul. To honor Karl Lagerfeld, we decided to add a Fleur De Lis charm to mirror his tie charm.

Products I used: 

▫️Apply a coat of OPI GelColor Stay Classic Base Coat

▫️Apply 2 coats of OPI GelColor in #BareMySoul

▫️Apply a coat of OPI GelColor Stay Shiny Top Coat

▫️Wipe the stickiness off with alcohol wipes

▫️Rub OPI Chrome Effects in #TinManCan onto the nails

▫️Place the Fleur De Lis charm on each middle finger

▫️Apply a coat of OPI GelColor Stay Shiny Top Coat

@opi @opi_professionals #OPIObsessed #AskForOPI #ad

Hair: @daniellepriano 
Makeup: @patmcgrathreal 
Nails: @nailsbyzola using @opi
Stylist: @mimicuttrell

@sydney_sweeney x @miumiu #MetGala2023 

Dipped in Crystals ✨✨✨ We wanted to mimic Sydney’s beautiful embellished Miu Miu gown on her nails by creating a crystal ombre look. For the base nude color, we opted for something sheer and skin-like. I used my ultimate favorite combo Bubble Bath, topped with Bare My Soul to create the chic and classic look. To make it even more glamorous, we added crystals. The look perfectly tied into the Met theme of timeless fashion.

Products I used: 

▫️ Apply a coat of OPI GelColor Stay Strong Base Coat

▫️ Apply one coat of OPI GelColor in #BubbleBath

▫️ Apply one coat of OPI GelColor in #BareMySoul

▫️ Apply a coat of OPI GelColor Stay Shiny Top Coat

▫️ Place the gems 💎

@sabrinacarpenter holographic mani for VMAs 2023 

Considering Sabrina had two different looks for the night, we wanted to create a manicure that seamlessly complimented both her jewel-studded performance look and glamorous red carpet ensemble. Pulling inspiration from her journey on tour, we opted for a pop of sparkle to capture the essence of her ‘Bejeweled Era’ which perfectly complimented her silver-studded gown.

Products I used: @opi @opi_professionals

▫️ Apply one coat of OPI GelColor Stay Strong Base Coat

▫️ Next, apply two coats of OPI GelColor in “I Cancer-tainly Shine” from the new OPI Big Zodiac Energy Collection

▫️ Apply one coat of OPI GelColor Stay Shiny Top Coat then wipe the nails with alcohol wipes

▫️ Rub in OPI Chrome Effects in “Mixed Metals” 

▫️ Finish with one coat of OPI GelColor Stay Shiny Top Coat

#OPIObsessed #AskForOPI

Timeless mani for @madelyncline VMAs 2023

To capture her natural and timeless beauty, we went with my go-to classic OPI shades to create an elegant manicure that complimented Madelyn’s stunning beige Givenchy gown. The subtle ombrè manicure felt like the perfect way to bring sophistication into her overall look. I always have these shades in my kit!

Products I used: @opi @opi_professionals

▫️ Apply 1 coat of OPI GelColor Stay Strong Base Coat

▫️ Apply 2 coats of OPI GelColor in “Put It In Neutral”

▫️ Apply 1 coat of OPI GelColor in “Alpine Snow” on the tip of the nails and gently smooth it out using ombré brush

▫️ Apply 1 coat of OPI GelColor in “Funny Bunny” on the tip of the nails and gently smooth it out using ombré brush

▫️ Apply one coat of OPI GeColor Stay Shiny Top Coat
